Streakers, stars and, now, a stunning smack: The Academy Awards moments we won't forget

When Will Smith marched onto the Oscars stage and smacked Chris Rock, the unpredictable moment served as a jarring interruption to Hollywood’s feel-good celebration and joined a long history of Academy Award controversy. Here's a look back at some Oscar top moments, stars and outfits.
